Package football

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Invitation
    The Invitation class implements an application that creates invitations which will be send from players to each other.
    Main
    The Main class implements an application that show the user his menu with the allowed operations for this user which based on his role.
    Notification
    The Notification class implements an application that creates notification that tells the playground owner that player payed for him.
    Payment
    The Payment class implements an application that withdraws ,deposits in eWallet, and shows payer and payee.
    Playground
    The Playground class implements an application that creates playgrounds for playground owner.
    Reservation
    The Reservation class implements an application that creates a reservation for specific playground in specific time.
    Team
    The Team class implements an application that creates team for the player, and modify it.
    User
    The User class implements an application that creates a user account for this application which can be a player, playground owner ,or administrator.
    Validation
    The Validation class implements an application that handle the inputs which taken from user.
